{"tid":336061,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 慢煮印度咖喱羊膝配黃薑飯","createTime":"2017-07-26T06:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T09:03:39.000Z","uid":30742,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"157c3d67aae9e011fc2cb2c52037dc76c8e678c7","tid":336061,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/aEJw2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FaEJw2.jpg&h=7a4f21d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aXUXccNGeP0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaXUXccNGeP0&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=69c26775\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aXUXccNGeP0</a><br />\n<br />\n之前在做印度牛肉咖喱時，已經想做羊肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前周三特價日行吉仔見到有羊膝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買左兩隻返去試下（原來凍肉鋪仲靚仲平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n有羊就梗係想做印式，但想唔好熟到柴，又梗係用慢煮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n果然如我想像中的嫩口，仲有靚靚粉紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n加埋黃薑飯一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n誠意推介一定要整埋個青瓜乳酪醬，我覺得點呢個真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慢煮印度咖喱羊膝配黃薑飯： <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/07/sous-indian-style-lamb-leg.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F07%2Fsous-indian-style-lamb-leg.html&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=012a8d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/07/sous-indian-style-lamb-leg.html</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3e5ade9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=bd9d24ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=4b2291db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"f2efa58ad7a40cfe8a7e997508dc8863c301a227","tid":336061,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d93664bedac07f536b856543e06a8c8be6f9133","tid":336061,"uid":45442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:09:43.000Z","msg":"有無人試過淘寶慢煮棒？"},{"pid":"e098d85cea8afc87ad2c3b32bb4dd952bd9cbfcd","tid":336061,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"想買慢煮棒但好貴 差唔多成千蚊<img src=\"/as