s/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似好抵，好想買返個嚟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買啦買啦！！呢個真心推介！真係好好用～</blockquote><br />\n依枝anova依家賣緊859 抵唔抵屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe46cf13bc04e4ec76cc79f13b8cc2483fe15de","tid":336061,"uid":851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"又係你呀老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名學野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b89a65bccb1fb33220f535543991fa9ea8a5bda","tid":336061,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>58度可以煮熟肉類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://winniekitchenwork.blogspot.hk/2016/06/the-science-of-sous-vide.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwinniekitchenwork.blogspot.hk%2F2016%2F06%2Fthe-science-of-sous-vide.html%3Fm%3D1&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5cee95b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://winniekitchenwork.blogspot.hk/2016/06/the-science-of-sous-vide.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n睇你點睇熟既定義！<br />\n如果係殺死細菌<br />\n每種肉所要求既溫度都唔同！蛋白質分解所需時間都唔同！<br />\n<br />\n慢煮真係科學黎！仲要慢慢研究！</blockquote><br />\n部份細菌呢個溫度唔足似殺死好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161216/s00005/1481824679578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161216%2Fs00005%2F1481824679578&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a9f0edc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161216%2Fs00005%2F1481824679578&h=6fe01d82\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161216/s00005/1481824679578</a><br />\n<br />\n2014年食物安全中心發表了「慢煮與食物安全 」報告，為確保食物安全，食物安全中心建議，「把食物浸煮至中心溫度達75℃，並保持30秒，以消滅致病菌；或相當溫度／時間組合，例如65℃維持10分鐘；70℃維持2分鐘等，但不應少於60℃達45分鐘」。<br />\n<br />\n我相信溫度同時間同肉既種類都要互相配合！<br />\n<br />\n當然好難一概而輪，亦不能夠迫人相信慢煮完全安全<br />\n正如牛羊粉紅色係肌紅蛋白而唔係血～有d人就算你講一百次佢都係唔ok～<br />\n同偏食一樣～無得迫～"},{"pid":"83c27f1b47166f63acbee084d6e175238c4afd81","tid":336061,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老娘點睇依款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無伏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係用呢款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n藍芽版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似好抵，好想買返個嚟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買啦買啦！！呢個真心推介！真係好好用～</blockquote><br />\n依枝anova依家賣緊859 抵唔抵屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都ok啦～～<br />\n之前好似要過千架～<br />\n如果而家唔買可能要等到聖誕先有大減價了！"},{"pid":"70d80a1506dd6c5662989516b3a2af6c4ffe566f","tid":336061,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:40:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係你呀老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名學野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388d3a7